item.title: Netflix Announces Byeon Woo-seok as Sung Jin-woo in Live-Action Solo Leveling
item.description: Netflix has officially announced its live-action Solo Leveling series with Byeon Woo-seok cast as Sung Jin-woo. Directed by Lee Hae-jun and Kim Byung-seo in collaboration with Kakao Entertainment.
